title: BullyBillows Double Ended Dog Lead | Multi-Functional Lead | Medium or Long Length for Obedience Work or Distance Training | Khaki
features: Multi-Functional Training Lead – Designed for versatility, this BullyBillows Double Ended Dog Lead is perfect for obedience training, distance work, and everyday walks.
Adjustable Length Options – Choose between medium or long lengths to suit your dog's training needs, providing flexibility for control or freedom.
Double-Ended Design – Features dual clips, allowing attachment to multiple points for balanced handling, hands-free use, or dual-dog walking.
Premium Durability – Made from high-quality, heavy-duty materials, ensuring long-lasting strength and reliability for all breeds and sizes.
Comfort & Control – Soft yet sturdy construction provides a secure grip, reducing strain on your hands while maintaining excellent control over your dog.
